date.textblock: Room 420, East West Towers, 4330 East West Highway, Bethesda, Maryland.

The staff will brief the Commission on the additional test data relevant to certain public comments received on the previously proposed revisions to the Commission's requirements for child-resistant packaging and on a draft
notice that would publish the new data for public comment.
For a recorded message containing the latest agenda information, call (301) 504-0709.
